  <brief_title>Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of ID1201 for Dose-finding in Mild Alzheimer's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Phase II Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of ID1201 for Dose-finding in Mild Alzheimer's Disease</official_title>
